    "At the same time, the game makes it possible to work on the patient's compliance with the rules and ability to wait.",
    "The game is administered in the clinic, through the use of HTC VIVE (HTC, 2023a) with the addition of a wireless adapter (HTC, 2023b), giving the user the possibility to move freely in the virtual space as if moving in the real space.",
    "The game is projected onto a large screen, allowing the therapist to follow the patient's execution of the tasks in real time and assess their progress.",
    "Three different cartoon-style settings have been developed: a child's bedroom, a garden, a school classroom.",
